landscape in the mist ( greek : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; , translit . &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1988 greek drama film directed by theodoros angelopoulos . it is based on the novel of the same name by theodoros angelopoulos . the film was selected as the greek entry for the best foreign language film at the 61st academy awards , but was not accepted as a nominee .